Package: purrrallel
Type: Package
Title: Parallelised Purrr
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Craig", "Gower", , "craig.gower@roche.com", c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Craig Gower <craig.gower@roche.com>
Description: This package is a light weight wrapper around the parallel package to provide
    functions with identical names and functionality to the purrr package but are fundermentally
    parallelised. If no cluster has been setup these functions will just call their purrr
    counterparts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
